		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津使用手上的梦想一心，进行至多5段的普通攻击，5段普攻依次造成<span color="#ffacff">8.3%,<br/>8.3%,16.6%,8.3%x2,16.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="447" width="413" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">离祸津较远时，祸津迅速朝玩家冲击，并施放两段斩击，冲击造成<span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，两段斩击分别造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%,58.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津旋转梦想一心，替换武器为<span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans" color="#ffdc72">薙</span><span color="#ffdc72">草之稻光</span><span>，同时在其前方产生一道落雷，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，之后场景间歇出现祸眼，触碰造成4段</span><span color="#ffacff">5.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">在祸津技能间歇期时攻击，产生雷盾，抵挡伤害；受击超4次时，每次攻击会增加10%反击概率；反击时，先劈一刀造成<span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害，接着产生次元斩造成3段</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="439" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津召唤4个<span textDecoration="underline">幻影</span><span>奔向场地边缘，持续劈出雷刃。3个假幻影只劈一刀，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害，真幻影劈十字斩，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，真幻影击破后祸津御建</span><span color="#ffebbf">眩晕</span><span>，假幻影击破后有50%概率立即爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于祸津身后时，祸津御建立即转身斩击，造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="414" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津依次斩出3个雷轮，每个雷轮造成<span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害，最后水平劈出一道雷刃，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津进行旋斩、冲击、旋斩最多3段的普通攻击，3段普攻依次造成<span color="#ffacff">8.3%x2,<br/>16.6%,33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="437" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">眩晕时受击超8次时，将有48%的概率立即恢复，且每次受击都会增加6%恢复概率。祸津恢复<span color="#ffebbf">眩晕</span><span>后，在身边产生雷震击飞玩家，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害但不显示数字</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="438" height="229" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津用梦想一心画圈后将其举向天空，召唤9个雷球在场地边缘，以顺时针顺序下落，雷球下落造成<span color="#ffacff">66.6%</span><span>伤害，留下雷痕，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">12.5%</span><span>伤害；<br/>雷球全部落下后祸津御建在场地中间施放次元斩，造成4段</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，最后碎屏斩造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
